{"type": "article", "id": 30412, "title": "CK进入Raf Simons时代，以及， adidas又推出了联名款｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-02T04:01:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 1780, "name": "CK"}, {"id": 2041, "name": "Jimmy Choo"}, {"id": 2382, "name": "新秀丽"}, {"id": 2819, "name": "Marc Newson"}, {"id": 4703, "name": "刘雯"}, {"id": 4799, "name": "鹿晗"}, {"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 18988, "name": "TUMI"}, {"id": 24118, "name": "侃爷"}, {"id": 25410, "name": "PVH"}, {"id": 30926, "name": "Giorgio Armani Foundation"}, {"id": 30927, "name": "Fjällräven"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160802101053dJGh5YluO8a73ET4.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/pvh-said-near-naming-raf-simons-to-calvin-klein-to-tap-raf-simons-10498197/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raf Simons 本周正式出任 &nbsp;Calvin Klein 创意总监一职</a>｜PVH 集团发表声明， Raf Simons 将到任 CK。此前， Raf Simons 从 Christian Dior 离职，他在 CK 将负责男装内衣、香水、牛仔、配饰、男女装的工作。此外，他有可能还会参与到&nbsp; Calvin Klein 广告创意。有信息称，他的年薪是 2000 万美元。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/giorgio-armani-foundation-10498616/\" rel=\"nofollow\">为了集团传承，82 岁的 Giorgio Armani 成立同名基金 Giorgio Armani Foundation</a>｜Giorgio Armani 一直是集团唯一股东，不仅同时肩负着董事会主席、首席执行官和创意总监多重职务，领导集团旗下时装、配件、美容、家具和房地产等多元业务，而且一直是集团唯一股东。基金会的成立是为了保护集团资产，确保这些资产在提倡的原则下维持稳定运行。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/financial/tumi-eyeing-future-samsonite-mergers-acquisitions-heineken-fashion-accessories-10498977/\" rel=\"nofollow\">新秀丽收购了 Tumi</a>｜昨日，全球最大品牌行李箱制造商 Samsonite International SA 新秀丽国际有限公司以约 18.24 亿美元完成对 Tumi Holdings Inc. 的收购。这也是新秀丽历史上最大的一次并购案，为此它寻求了约 24.25 亿美元的融资。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/focus/athletic-outdoor/kanye-west-bbc-radio-interview-adidas-shoes-245473/\" rel=\"nofollow\">侃爷说想要做价格在 30 美元以下的球鞋&nbsp;</a>｜昨天在 BBC 电台做节目时，侃爷提到想和阿迪达斯合作生产价格更便宜的球鞋。之前他的 Yeezy Boost 350 和 750 价格分别为 200 美元和 350 美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.urbanoutfitters.com/urban/index.jsp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Urban Outfitters 和 adidas 推出联名款</a>，名为 “We the Future”，8 月 1 日开卖——不过，这色调真的不是冲着 80 年代怀旧去的？<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020903542xjp7qRY5lngu3hW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020904358m7yPBFCvgGz0X5h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501340\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090449EzHAlB0UGQFM9JvK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572618\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020905042L7Ee09GXWlbdiMf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020905152we3ocsLQABVPDad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501340\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090526JhTfNC6avXA0WMBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090535uxXUagsjZyeWVGMh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090544617lK0esHQSjhdF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501340\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020906022GlDJWbFO7fpnjev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090642NKe6GHv4ZnB0it5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090704lcvFKrR5GNi70Yyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090739qM21kKYUEWBjc4bf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802090759DPvFxARGwgNfMk0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fjallraven.com/re-kanken-550-1-size\" rel=\"nofollow\">瑞典品牌 Fjällräven 推出新系列 Re-Kånken，有 11 个配色。</a>整个系列以环保为设计概念，背包部分的制作材料由可回收循环再用的聚酯塑胶瓶所制成。（但其实样子和 Fjällräven 普通包长得差不多）</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020927484phrSkLg5F03GZyM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802093145f4Y8V9rkKDUlpuxI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.731922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802093236gTehjMzUpPWFslbB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802093256YigK3UwWm4HLNQcC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/lu-han-liu-wen-for-puma-2016-fall-t7-suede\" rel=\"nofollow\">鹿晗与刘雯为 PUMA 2016 秋季 T7 运动装与 Suede 鞋款系列打广告。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221220XC2vbV7MngZeciYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221537MZF6IPsOWxNTykHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/jimmy-choo-couples-shoes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jimmy Choo 也推出了运动鞋，还是情侣款。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608012219511yg6bwlOjZSe8DEp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222111qwD1rXl0CZ3zAKU8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222119bwUxq54rDHjVACdQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222128DGmV0IljHN5QabUC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">继两年前的毛毛背包后，<a href=\"http://www.lifestyleasia.com/sg/en/travel/photo-story/louis-vuitton-collaborates-with-marc-newson-on-new-rolling-luggage/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Louis Vuitton 和 Marc Newson 又联手设计了一款行李箱，</a>用上了 LV 经典的 Monogram 图案。Marc Newson 用了 18 个月做研发，用了轻化物料，使这款行李箱比一般 LV 行李箱轻了一半，但多出 15% 容量。另外，这也是 LV 推出的一款四轮行李箱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802095134QqzvnsMWw61Chy4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608020952040JKgpYUbHOjEAPiD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666282\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Childs 刚发布了 2017 年春夏 Lookbook。这个品牌成立于 2016 年，刚推出了两季，想要在做有“现代”、“经典”又“不追逐潮流”的男装。来看看。想看官网<a href=\"http://www.childsnewyork.com/2017-ss/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点这里</a>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100332fHt7bWCKsvThJxUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100343KYQVxnmhwb3ze98I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100354jhvJ0zpd4FgGwYxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100403FlN5tf6qe4iJ8AgP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100413o6ErAstFu0fRCxK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100423rhTFLs6R1NvWz9GE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802100437XZ87yHPGuJjD5f4M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}